name: ONIMATA-06
description:
ONIMATA-06
TEIKO IS HERE TO END YOUR FEAR

Set of 4
2 of 4

TEIKO is a group of ONIMATA where all the crew believes that their duty is to protect the weak, to revolt and never obey the current made up law. But sometimes they took the wrong way to do what they believe is right 

---------------

ONIMATA PROJECT (オニマタ) is my visual storytelling project that felling stories about a group of demons who survived the post apocalyptic world which caused by the unknown organization.

ONI means demon in Japanese, and MATA means eye in Bahasa Indonesia.
